oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Land Survey, Portion of Henry Merritt Property
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Land survey of a portion of the Henry Merritt property. The property is located at the corner of Pettus Street and Hornberger Lane. The survey shows a Tennessee Central Railroad track along the southeast edge of the property.
